data.title: Family & General Dentist in Ellenton, FL
data.meta_description: If you are looking for a family dentist to take your family to come to our dental office today. We offer services such as periodontal, general, cosmetic, and much more. Call our office to make an appointment today!
data.text:
Dr. Whaley was raised in the rural town of Milford, Delaware. He grew up loving the outdoors and beaches of the mid-Atlantic. He attended the University of Miami and earned a bachelor of science degree in biology. Dr. Whaley then went on to attend dental school at the University of Maryland College of Dental Surgery, the first dental school in the world and currently, one of the top-ranked.

Dr. Whaley has been serving the Ellenton community for many years and has established a 5-star reputation among his patients. He loves helping people smile and looks forward to meeting you as a new patient.

Dr. Wasef believes that dentistry is an art, and she loves the impact it has on people’s lives. She studied at the Nova Southeastern University College of Dental Medicine. She moved back to the West coast of Florida to be closer to her hometown, Clearwater, Florida. When she is not in the office caring for patients, she enjoys running and biking outdoors, working out, going to the beach, and traveling with her husband to learn about different cultures.

Welcome to Ellenton Family, a modern, high-tech dental office in Ellenton, Florida. Our warm, welcoming team looks forward to meeting you, and we hope you’ll enjoy our unique amenities including flat-screen TVs with Netflix in patient rooms, massage chairs, blankets and pillows, and warm, scented towels!

Dr. Whaley holds himself and his team to the highest standards. Patient comfort is a top priority, and we want every patient to feel satisfied with the care they receive. Whether you come in for general, cosmetic or restorative dental care, you can feel confident in the friendly, knowledgeable team at Ellenton Family Dental.

Here at Ellenton Family Dental, we understand the importance of a beautiful smile. With cosmetic dentistry services, we can enhance your teeth, leaving you with a smile that you can be proud of for years to come. Let us know what you would like to improve, and we will work with you to provide the perfect solution.

At Ellenton Family Dental, we are committed to your comfort during dental treatments. Our doctors are kind and gentle, and we offer sedation dentistry options that can ease pain and calm anxiety and fear. To accommodate a variety of needs, we offer laughing gas, oral sedation, and local anesthesia.
